    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RIG Riot is a roguelike third-person mech-action shooter. Fight increasingly difficult enemies while completing objectives, level up, and choose the Weapons and Volatile Mods that will let you return from your raids victorious. Discover thousands of permanent parts, and build a RIG unlike any other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exciting Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat can feel quite different depending on the style of RIG you build. Do you prefer a light and mobile mech that bombards their foes from range with a trusty sniper? How about a well-rounded powerhouse who focuses on bringing the pain with missile bombardments and automatic rifles? Or maybe you prefer a tanky build that barrels through all opposition with laser blades and shotguns? Put together your build and then prepare for fast-paced combat against a wide array of enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180340/extras/b01830589a50181cffd31c5ca74eb17e.poster.avif?t=1771952857\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180340/extras/b01830589a50181cffd31c5ca74eb17e.webm?t=1771952857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180340/extras/b01830589a50181cffd31c5ca74eb17e.mp4?t=1771952857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deep Customization</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In RIG Riot, every loss is an opportunity. Dive into the garage and check out the exciting new parts you've earned. Every part in RIG Riot is made out of a combination of components from the various full sets available in the game. There are an incredible amount of parts to find- which will you use?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180340/extras/5a401456e5ac3b4b2d4f3253ecb8f920.poster.avif?t=1771952857\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180340/extras/5a401456e5ac3b4b2d4f3253ecb8f920.webm?t=1771952857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180340/extras/5a401456e5ac3b4b2d4f3253ecb8f920.mp4?t=1771952857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Powerful Synergies </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finds the best ways to make your unique RIG shine as you travel through increasingly difficult stages. Search for rare weapons and mods with effects that compliment your build to see just how far you can go.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180340/extras/d464eaa5fef1a81d57995bbc4fe2a46d.poster.avif?t=1771952857\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180340/extras/d464eaa5fef1a81d57995bbc4fe2a46d.webm?t=1771952857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180340/extras/d464eaa5fef1a81d57995bbc4fe2a46d.mp4?t=1771952857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  </h2>",
